    {
      "name": "browser-open",
      "description": "Open a URL in Holo Browser's content-addressed loader and return a self-verifying snapshot: the served/minted κ (a did:holo you re-derive, Law L5), final URL, title, extracted text and links. Accepts holo://κ, ipfs://, ENS .eth and http(s) (a live page is fetched once and minted into a κ).",
